{"tid":26094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婚禮拒絕共舞　慘遭開槍擊斃","createTime":"2016-12-06T13:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T13:44:18.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd05ac03d8992c92536980a4dc121fbbdb6da995","tid":26094,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:44:18.000Z","msg":"印度北部上周六一個婚宴發生槍擊案，女舞蹈員竟因為拒絕醉客的共舞要求，慘遭射殺。<br />\n<br />\n手機拍到的片段顯示，24歲的卡爾溫德（Kulwinder Kaur）腹部中槍，在台上應聲倒下，送院途中證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n《印度快報》報導，警方表示，兇手比拉（Billa）是新郎的朋友，當天喝醉後向天開槍，並要求上台與舞蹈團共舞，但被阻止，於是向卡爾溫德開槍。警方在現場撿獲槍支，比拉目前在逃被通緝。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/214333_3b7548f07f097b10ac9cd1f8ea266fd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F214333_3b7548f07f097b10ac9cd1f8ea266fd9.jpg&h=7963660a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UX3E32W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUX3E32W.jpg&h=bdd78fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breaking-news/international/20161206/46643658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Fbreaking-news%2Finternational%2F20161206%2F46643658&d=oDJDpIHLa9AwnnxG9wFnJwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=036eae93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breaking-news/international/20161206/46643658</a>"}]}